               <item corresp="#div1-lb2" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>2</ref>
            <p>The nomen sacrum Ἰησοῦ is written as ιυ with horizontal bar above (both times)</p>
          </item>
               <item corresp="#div1-lb3" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>3</ref>
            <p>The nomen sacrum Ἰησοῦ is written as ιυ with horizontal bar above</p>
          </item>
               <item corresp="#div1-lb4" xml:space="preserve">
            <ref>4</ref>
            <p>πνεύματος is written as πνα with horizontal bar above; πατρὸς is written as a nomen sacrum (i.e., πρς with horizontal bar above); υἱοῦ is written as a nomen sacrum (i.e., υυ with horizontal bar above)</p>
          </item>
